    ns1:otherInformation "The course is designed for continuous assessment, with numerous classroom activities to apply the content of the programme. Throughout the course there will be collaborative work, exercises, Moodle questionnaires, application and assessment tests. Due to the technical nature of the subject, it is not recommended that students be assessed solely by a final exam."@es ;
